<s> A possibly forgotten technique in testing WCAG 2.0-- one we discussed a lot back in September-- is personas or personae, or composite hypothetical users.  </s>
<s> I found an accessibility-related paper that deals with personas, in this case concerning cellphones: (Google the URL for HTML version) The research isn't done yet, but at least it's there.  </s>
